quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,146,"Abo twahaye igitabo baramuzi (Muhamadi n’ibigwi bye) nk’uko bazi abana babo. Ndetse mu by’ukuri, bamwe muri bo bahisha ukuri kandi bakuzi"
  2,147,"Ukuri nyako ni uguturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe, ku bw’ibyo ntukabe mu bashidikanya"
  2,148,"Na buri bantu bafite icyerekezo berekeramo (basenga), ngaho nimurushanwe mu gukora ibyiza, kandi aho muzaba muri hose Allah azabahuriza hamwe mwese (ku munsi w’imperuka). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  2,149,"Kandi aho uzajya hose (ugashaka gusenga) ujye werekeza uburanga bwawe ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Al Ka’aba). Mu by’ukuri, (kuwerekeraho) ni ukuri guturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe. Kandi Allah ntabwo ayobewe ibyo mukora"
  2,150,"Kandi naho uzajya hose (ugashaka gusenga) ujye werekeza uburanga bwawe ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Al Ka’aba). Naho muzaba muri hose (mugashaka gusenga) mujye muwerekezaho uburanga bwanyu, kugira ngo abantu batazabagiraho urwitwazo, uretse abahuguje (roho zabo) muri bo (bazahora mu mpaka). Bityo ntimuzabatinye ahubwo mujye mutinya njye; kugira ngo mbahundagazeho inema zanjye no kugira ngo muyoboke"
  2,151,"Ni nako twaboherejemo Intumwa ibakomokamo, ibasomera imirongo yacu (Qur’an), ibeza (imitima), ibigisha igitabo (Qur’an) n’ubushishozi (imigenzo y’Intumwa n’amategeko y’idini), ndetse ikanabigisha ibyo mutari muzi"
  2,152,Ngaho nimunyibuke (munsingiza); nanjye nzabibuka (nzabazirikana). Kandi munshimire ntimuzampakane
  2,153,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwifashishe ukwihangana n’amasengesho. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ari kumwe n’abihangana"